             TO  RJL0008-GROUP-CO-CD

      *   기준년월일
           MOVE  WK-H-I-BASE-YMD
             TO  RJL0008-BASE-YMD

170224*   고객식별자
           MOVE  IN-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  RJL0008-CUST-IDNFR

      *   총자산
           MOVE  IN-JSC-AMT
             TO  RJL0008-TOTAL-ASST

      *   매출액
           MOVE  IN-MCA-AMT
             TO  RJL0008-SALEPR

      *   기준년자기자본금
           MOVE  IN-JGJ-AMT
             TO  RJL0008-BASE-YR-ONCP-AMT

      *   금융비용차입금
           MOVE  IN-GBC-AMT
             TO  RJL0008-FNCS-AMBR

      *   당행차입금
           MOVE  ZERO
             TO  RJL0008-OWBNK-AMBR

      *   영업현금흐름액
           MOVE  IN-YHH-AMT
             TO  RJL0008-BZOPR-ACF

      *   업체평균이자율
           MOVE  WK-ENTP-AVG-INT-RT
             TO  RJL0008-ENTP-AVG-INT-RT

      *   여신성자산한도
           MOVE  WK-LNBZ-I-ASST-CLAM
             TO  RJL0008-LNBZ-I-ASST-CLAM

      *   신용등급지원비율
           MOVE  IN-GWBY
             TO  RJL0008-CRDRAT-SPORT-RATO

      *   자기자본기준금액
           MOVE  WK-ONCP-BSAMT
             TO  RJL0008-ONCP-BSAMT

      *   영업활동기준한도
           MOVE  WK-BZOPR-A-BASE-CLAM
             TO  RJL0008-BZOPR-A-BASE-CLAM

      *   포괄설정가능금액
           MOVE  WK-INLS-STUP-ABLAMT
             TO  RJL0008-INLS-STUP-ABLAMT

      *   시스템최종처리일시
           MOVE  BICOM-TRAN-START-YMS
             TO  RJL0008-SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS

      *   시스템최종사용자번호
           MOVE  BICOM-USER-EMPID
             TO  RJL0008-SYS-LAST-UNO
